        "cooked": "<p>I may have missed this, but did Ramonet change their label in 2013? Note the Ramonet J-C. Just curious.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/6/2/626e7896ac19cc36a00d24a8e0967d09b17d5a16.jpeg\" alt=\"image.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"e2LtsNPfUqGw1NtZpxfeKDaTrO6\" width=\"360\" height=\"480\"><br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/7/9/798cd347374514f6765a673c4f7f1d5c0ff52756.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1065 (1).JPG\" data-base62-sha1=\"hlhuqroknsXD71K9sDuo7tgrV0G\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\"></p>",
