        "id": 1895932,
        "name": "William Kelley",
        "username": "William_Kelley",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-03-27T23:14:51.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The Domaine has been restructured. As I understand it, the Domaine\u2019s holdings have been split between Jean-Claude and Noel; and Noel now sells his grapes to Jean-Claude and acts solely as a viticulturalist, with Jean-Claude now making the wine.</p>\n<p>However, I had been under the impression that the 2013 wines would continue to have the usual Domaine Ramonet label. Mine are still in storage so I haven\u2019t actually seen them. But I thought the new label was due to begin with the 2014s\u2026</p>",
